1
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:57,000
So it was her.

2
00:01:57,800 --> 00:01:59,930
Liu Mianmian was the one who killed me.

3
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:07,720
Broken vase.

4
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:12,680
Your Majesty, what's wrong?

5
00:02:13,040 --> 00:02:13,960
Hanxing.

6
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:16,960
So it was you who sent me the news

7
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:19,160
that the Empress left the palace early.

8
00:02:19,880 --> 00:02:21,000
Who could it be?

9
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:22,040
Your Majesty,

10
00:02:22,160 --> 00:02:23,560
did you have a nightmare?

11
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:25,200
Your Majesty,

12
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:27,720
His Majesty is hosting a palace banquet at Qinghuan Pavilion tonight

13
00:02:27,720 --> 00:02:29,180
and invites you to attend.

14
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:32,329
It seems I've been reborn back to before the banquet.

15
00:02:39,440 --> 00:02:41,760
Liu Mianmian deliberately wore that jade pendant to kill me

16
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:42,880
to frame Li Yunxi.

17
00:02:43,320 --> 00:02:44,800
It seems Li Yunxi and I

18
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:46,360
have many misunderstandings.

19
00:02:46,360 --> 00:02:47,720
So it was you who sent me the news

20
00:02:47,720 --> 00:02:49,920
that the Empress left the palace early.

21
00:02:51,200 --> 00:02:53,000
Who exactly is the spy by my side?

22
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:55,079
And who instructed them?

23
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:56,530
In this life,

24
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:58,440
I must find out the truth.

25
00:02:59,720 --> 00:03:00,480
Yunxi.

26
00:03:01,320 --> 00:03:03,180
Perhaps as the mystery unravels,

27
00:03:03,720 --> 00:03:05,080
we can reconcile.

28
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:08,760
Your Majesty,

29
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:10,440
the Empress is feeling unwell.

30
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:13,040
She cannot attend the palace banquet tonight.

31
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:15,100
She's feeling unwell.

32
00:03:16,079 --> 00:03:17,640
Has she seen an imperial physician?

33
00:03:17,640 --> 00:03:18,400
Your Majesty,

34
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:20,860
you haven't visited the Empress for a month.

35
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:22,800
Why not go see her yourself?

36
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:26,410
I am not a physician.

37
00:03:26,720 --> 00:03:28,120
It's useless for me to go.

38
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:29,600
Coward.

39
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:36,690
I will take my leave.

40
00:03:40,920 --> 00:03:42,450
Aren't you feeling unwell?

41
00:03:43,320 --> 00:03:44,560
You look fine to me.

42
00:03:48,079 --> 00:03:48,940
I was faking it.

43
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:51,850
I didn't want to go to the banquet tonight.

44
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:55,240
Xiao Ling,

45
00:03:56,079 --> 00:03:59,079
do you know that is the crime of deceiving the Emperor?

46
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:05,960
What is she doing?

47
00:04:08,040 --> 00:04:09,100
What are you doing?

48
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:10,480
Let me ask you,

49
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:13,560
how many times have we kissed?

50
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:25,360
How improper!

51
00:04:27,440 --> 00:04:28,700
Why are you so nervous?

52
00:04:29,360 --> 00:04:30,240
Could it be that

53
00:04:30,880 --> 00:04:31,800
you love me

54
00:04:32,840 --> 00:04:34,770
and not your precious Consort Xue?

55
00:04:39,640 --> 00:04:40,400
Tell me,

56
00:04:41,080 --> 00:04:42,740
how many times have we kissed?

57
00:04:45,800 --> 00:04:47,440
We've been married for two years.

58
00:04:47,440 --> 00:04:49,440
Every time, you either chased me out with a knife

59
00:04:49,440 --> 00:04:50,900
or splashed me with water.

60
00:04:51,080 --> 00:04:52,610
We haven't even held hands,

61
00:04:53,760 --> 00:04:55,360
let alone kissed.

62
00:04:56,400 --> 00:04:58,730
Li Yunxi doesn't remember that we kissed.

63
00:04:59,280 --> 00:05:01,200
It seems he doesn't have the memories of these two lifetimes.

64
00:05:01,200 --> 00:05:02,930
I'm the only one who was reborn.

65
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:04,960
This is going to be fun.

66
00:05:15,440 --> 00:05:16,560
You gave it to me.

67
00:05:17,520 --> 00:05:18,640
So it's mine.

68
00:05:19,880 --> 00:05:21,320
No one can take it away.

69
00:05:22,520 --> 00:05:24,720
He cares so much about this jade pendant.

70
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:27,120
That means he still cares about me a little.

71
00:05:27,320 --> 00:05:29,850
Then what is going on with him and Consort Xue?

72
00:05:30,520 --> 00:05:32,450
Is there something you're hiding?

73
00:05:35,960 --> 00:05:37,600
If you gave it to me, it's mine.

74
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:39,730
Don't even think about taking it back.

75
00:05:41,560 --> 00:05:42,640
You won't say, right?

76
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:44,040
I can find out myself.

77
00:05:44,680 --> 00:05:46,740
I'll see what you're keeping from me.

78
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:49,340
I'm going back to Jile Hall first.

79
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:51,120
What about the palace banquet?

80
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:51,920
I'm not going.

81
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:53,380
I don't want to see her.

82
00:06:16,880 --> 00:06:18,880
She actually dared to pinch My face.

83
00:06:18,880 --> 00:06:19,740
Such audacity.

84
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,920
Truly audacious.

85
00:06:31,400 --> 00:06:33,520
Your Highness dressed up specifically today.

86
00:06:33,520 --> 00:06:35,320
Are you going to see His Majesty?

87
00:06:41,840 --> 00:06:42,400
Hanxing.

88
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:44,480
I haven't seen Prince Qi in a long time,

89
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:45,680
and I miss him dearly.

90
00:06:45,840 --> 00:06:46,920
Invite him over for a drink for me.

91
00:06:46,920 --> 00:06:47,840
Prince Qi.

92
00:06:53,520 --> 00:06:55,200
The Empress is really lucky.

93
00:06:56,760 --> 00:06:58,820
She happened to be unwell last night,

94
00:06:59,520 --> 00:07:01,200
which ruined my plans.

95
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:03,420
Your Highness.

96
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:04,800
In my opinion,

97
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:06,960
since the Empress isn't vying for favor,

98
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:08,800
living in peace is just fine.

99
00:07:08,960 --> 00:07:10,880
She doesn't vie for favor, yet she monopolizes His Majesty's heart.

100
00:07:10,880 --> 00:07:12,940
That makes her even more detestable.

101
00:07:23,520 --> 00:07:26,360
Ling and Mo are meeting today at the Hour of Shen.

102
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:30,520
It really fell right into my lap.

103
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:31,580
Your Highness,

104
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:33,920
who do you think has been secretly

105
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:36,000
sending you news about the Empress?

106
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:36,920
Who cares?

107
00:07:37,640 --> 00:07:38,840
All I know is that

108
00:07:39,440 --> 00:07:42,240
the news this person sends is always true.

109
00:07:53,400 --> 00:07:54,730
What are you doing here?

110
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:57,280
Greetings, Your Highness.

111
00:07:58,280 --> 00:08:00,320
I'll let you prance around a bit longer.

112
00:08:00,320 --> 00:08:01,600
Once I catch the spy,

113
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:03,340
I'll deal with you all at once.

114
00:08:10,280 --> 00:08:13,010
I heard you weren't feeling well, Your Highness.

115
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:15,960
I made some medicinal food to help you recover.

116
00:08:19,400 --> 00:08:20,000
Thank you.

117
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:22,480
But I don't like taking medicine,

118
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:23,740
nor do I like porridge.

119
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:26,240
Don't be afraid, Your Highness.

120
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:28,480
I didn't poison it.

121
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:34,720
I mean well.

122
00:08:34,919 --> 00:08:36,980
I only hope for your speedy recovery.

123
00:08:37,760 --> 00:08:40,490
Since you don't believe me, I shall take my leave.

124
00:08:48,800 --> 00:08:49,660
Your Highness,

125
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:51,500
why did you drink it yourself?

126
00:08:51,640 --> 00:08:52,900
What are we going to do?

127
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:54,620
What are you afraid of?

128
00:08:54,680 --> 00:08:56,920
It wasn't in the medicinal food anyway.

129
00:09:00,240 --> 00:09:01,400
You are brilliant, Your Highness.

130
00:09:01,400 --> 00:09:02,360
As for these pastries,

131
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:03,840
the Empress prepared them herself.

132
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:05,500
She will definitely eat them.

133
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:07,080
Keep a close watch.

134
00:09:07,520 --> 00:09:10,320
Once Li Yunmo enters the palace to see the Empress,

135
00:09:10,640 --> 00:09:13,370
I will invite His Majesty to catch them in the act.

136
00:09:59,640 --> 00:10:00,500
Your Highness,

137
00:10:00,520 --> 00:10:02,380
His Majesty will arrive shortly.

138
00:10:03,640 --> 00:10:04,280
Guards!

139
00:10:04,920 --> 00:10:06,480
Seize this adulterer!

140
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:09,920
Concubine Xue.

141
00:10:10,800 --> 00:10:11,520
Who are you?

142
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:14,720
I am Liusu, a maid from Jile Hall.

143
00:10:16,760 --> 00:10:19,000
Who did you think she was?

144
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:22,480
You were clearly poisoned with Qingsirao.

145
00:10:22,480 --> 00:10:23,740
How can you be so sober?

146
00:10:24,160 --> 00:10:25,280
How do you know

147
00:10:25,880 --> 00:10:27,400
I was poisoned with Qingsirao?

148
00:10:27,400 --> 00:10:28,120
Unless...

149
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:29,920
you administered it?

150
00:10:31,080 --> 00:10:34,800
You intentionally leaked word that you were drinking with Li Yunmo,

151
00:10:34,800 --> 00:10:37,730
but secretly you were waiting for me to take the bait.

152
00:10:39,680 --> 00:10:41,480
This was all a trap you set.

153
00:10:48,800 --> 00:10:50,040
How did you know

154
00:10:50,920 --> 00:10:52,920
Li Yunmo was coming to drink with me?

155
00:10:53,240 --> 00:10:55,040
Why do you think, Your Highness,

156
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:57,360
that I would tell you?

157
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:07,160
Guards!

158
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:15,400
The Emperor will be here any moment.

159
00:11:15,400 --> 00:11:16,530
Let's see who dares.

160
00:11:17,280 --> 00:11:19,640
I heard Your Majesty's harem was always harmonious.

161
00:11:19,640 --> 00:11:21,760
I didn't expect to have the chance today

162
00:11:21,760 --> 00:11:23,040
to watch such a drama.

163
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:29,720
Prince Qi, you suddenly came to the palace to play chess with me.

164
00:11:29,720 --> 00:11:31,980
And now you have followed me to Jile Hall.

165
00:11:32,160 --> 00:11:34,080
Did you already know what would happen?

166
00:11:34,080 --> 00:11:36,010
Empress, the more you want to know,

167
00:11:36,120 --> 00:11:37,450
the less I will tell you.

168
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:39,520
Your Majesty,

169
00:11:39,840 --> 00:11:41,880
aren't you going in to intervene?

170
00:11:42,680 --> 00:11:44,000
You simply wouldn't dare touch me.

171
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:46,400
Since ancient times, the strong rule over life and death,

172
00:11:46,400 --> 00:11:48,730
while the lives of the weak are worthless.

173
00:11:48,880 --> 00:11:50,400
Today, I will show you

174
00:11:51,480 --> 00:11:53,440
what it feels like to have your limbs broken.
